{"tid":1754251,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"由連登開始的連寵拯救隊正式上線啦！","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T11:44:19.000Z","uid":777,"like":185,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"121b77179f2e4c9f58ef4b6f61bd817a50f392ad","tid":1754251,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8MvrhM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8MvrhM.jpg&h=d1650a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日咁開心，終於有機會同大家介紹一吓我哋<br />\n<br />\n我哋係一班連登討論區組成嘅義工，<br />\n原先係由一位絲打因為種種原因而無意中做咗暫託，<br />\n但係一個人能力再強都抵唔過一個團隊，<br />\n所以開始萌生成立拯救隊嘅念頭。<br />\n<br />\n除咗令到更多嘅浪浪得到幫助，<br />\n同時一眾巴絲打又可以有主子嘅陪伴，<br />\n就係咁招募左一班義工，<br />\n希望可以用自己唔同嘅技能幫助有需要嘅浪浪，<br />\n令佢地唔需要再擔驚受怕。<br />\n<br />\n如需協助，歡迎你聯絡我哋<br />\n特別係TG重災區嘅動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅Tg Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/linkpethelper\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flinkpethelper&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=6617c3b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/linkpethelper</a><br />\n我哋嘅Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/linkanimalrescueteam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flinkanimalrescueteam%2F&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1cc27417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/linkanimalrescueteam/</a><br />\nInstagram : link.animal<br />\n<br />\n因為剛剛成立無耐，現時拯救隊物資短缺，十分需要大家嘅幫助，如果有任何物資/捐款歡迎pm 我哋，所有捐款使用我哋會每月公佈，請大家放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外亦希望有車人士同更多嘅暫托家庭可以幫忙<br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若希望成為伙伴之一<br />\n請填寫Google Form 表格<br />\n填寫後請PM我哋<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/7EUTYFQjGYYuJoQUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7EUTYFQjGYYuJoQUA&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=c1d97972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/7EUTYFQjGYYuJoQUA</a><br />\n<br />\n下面有我哋正在暫托之貓貓<br />\n全部正受社會化訓練同埋未隱定<br />\n未會出領養住<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"f6c6c33ed6a7010bc3eba2feba574d96db399201","tid":1754251,"uid":19145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[元朗屏山北][搞大佢]區選仲未完仲可以再爭取!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754167</a>"},{"pid":"efcb4d4967fe1c87970f3a6dcd2ff6fc6e0f1713","tid":1754251,"uid":201128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a961d038303e3e9b075c7305c4baf75aac9e4b77","tid":1754251,"uid":250948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcab479d39f2e0e2f88a84738cf56261905ed130","tid":1754251,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=4d1c1326\" data-auto-link target=\"_b