u7popolomo <br />\n<br />\n物資我哋係嚴重缺貓砂同埋籠<br />\n<br />\n感謝你地支援<br />\n<br />\n因仍有大量求助case <br />\n天氣開始轉凍<br />\n暫托位亦都係絕對唔夠<br />\n如你能夠成為暫托家庭亦都歡迎與我哋聯絡"},{"pid":"84d7058dc3d40ea547b32cbc9792d83d58cc953b","tid":1754251,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aeda987429b5b80fd28df5fbd44cdc0d3eef8883","tid":1754251,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e239e600f22e4c7270167380b5beafe6fc94ba","tid":1754251,"uid":147464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f01f7690d4aba186fa188d3154b02d7a1078ac45","tid":1754251,"uid":265880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"卒之有連貓！等咗好耐喇！"},{"pid":"8317f7549987ad361050e70b2b38d2ea5fa60e7c","tid":1754251,"uid":264433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"有幼貓用既貓砂盆，床，出街袋同罐罐 唔知你地有無需要呢？要糧或者其他物資都可以睇下幫唔幫到手"},{"pid":"605161dad4b59d0e3ae99149a73739fb9a4d383f","tid":1754251,"uid":122740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8bceea1cac709fdd78c188a1dbd7c689b4d5669","tid":1754251,"uid":156405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大大力推"},{"pid":"b1be46c0494904e5f0d555334d18e0641a541398","tid":1754251,"uid":10070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a23ba1f727471c77a9a31dc179c9ea938c4e65","tid":1754251,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:30:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62356b8424dd3230634018be47fc63ae671930c2","tid":1754251,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8317f7549987ad361050e70b2b38d2ea5fa60e7c","tid":1754251,"uid":264433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"有幼貓用既貓砂盆，床，出街袋同罐罐 唔知你地有無需要呢？要糧或者其他物資都可以睇下幫唔幫到手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"需要，請tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n@fkyouhk_gov"},{"pid":"f16e20d691af45fc7618fd547e14e4f59d51d6b6","tid":1754251,"uid":315545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88df2fdb991cc166e1a8e208f0da2ad9f09a2e0d","tid":1754251,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n📣 招募人員<br />\n<br />\n連寵是信念，<br />\n任何人都有機會可以成為連寵<br />\n<br />\n我們相信尊重和溝通，<br />\n尊重生命，尊重領養人，尊重伙伴。<br />\n辦法總比困難多。<br />\n溝通才能解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n現招募更多伙伴<br />\n拓展黃色版圖<br />\n<br />\n1. 現為動物義工，認同連寵理念<br />\n   不忘救助動物初心者<br />\n<br />\n2. 有意成為動物義工者，有肩膀有承擔<br />\n    願意聆聽和學習<br />\n<br />\n3. 現職Marketing / PR 行業<br />\n    亦有志出一分力者<br />\n    我們需要人手處理平台和一些事務<br />\n<br />\n4. 現職會計 / 法律相關行業人士<br />\n    亦有志出一分力者<br />\n    需要專業人士處理同顧問com sec<br />\n<br />\n5.  有車/有車隊人士<br />\n     需要車隊運送物資與動物來往貓舍<br />\n     成立初期真的缺乏資金<br />\n<br />\n6.  各區店舖老闆<br />\n     如能提供位置收集捐贈物資<br />\n     不勝感激<br />\n<br />\n如有意加入或查詢<br />\n請即PM @fkyouhk_gov<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"493215af4ccb22ac45167f8f3a504a0321079c4b","tid":1754251,"uid":57815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1f70548353a3b79eed2d910d0deb36afe61637","tid":1754251,"uid":323640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a42e5148bb3d0bc48df23cd101826cb0b2956b8f","tid":1754251,"uid":777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"#連寵要人<br />\n<br />\n📣招募貓舍義工<br />\n<br />\n平日上午邊個得閒🥺<br />\n特別缺人😢<br />\n<br />\n新手又好老手又好<br />\n幫到手就係好手足🙌🏻<br />\n<br />\n福利：<br />\n又學到野又有得撚貓<br />\n<br />\n有意聯絡 @hkvetnurse"},{"pid":"bae49d4d3a3c706fbbb72cfe5fa9a6894312a6aa","tid":1754251,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eeb738526fe04cea62e5e7aa94660bec4d414695","tid":1754251,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11710dcd8b557b2af5cc049bbced6d39431e898f","tid":1754251,"uid":248955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T01:24:24.000Z","msg":"推~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011f13b66db6b34935dedb78933fa08ef6cb00ed","tid":1754251,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eba2e9bf1c03151a844819b69837a3c7cd5eb9d5","tid":1754251,"uid":221492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f91a1329473df5cac33633ed04955b05679aed5","tid":1754251,"uid":140538,